
REQUIREMENT
---------------------------------
You will have to install the addon Extra Interfaces to configure IP-addresses 
to your virtual interfaces.

CHANGELOG
---------------------------------
0.2.1 / 24-11-2015
- Fixed couple of scripts to enable successful execution on IPCop 2.0 firewall

0.2.0 / 09-03-2010
- Add check for Extra Interfaces to installer
- Add check for Extra Interfaces to CGI
- Add description to VLANs
- Add edit function for description
- Add init options to rc.vlan

FILEINFO
---------------------------------
install             - Installation script
langs/de.pl         - German language file
langs/de.pl         - Englisch language file
rc.sysinit.patch    - patch for rc.sysinti
rc.vlan             - startup script to setup vlans
vlan.cgi            - vlan configuration CGI for WebGUI
vlan_helper         - used to run ./rc.vlan as root 
vlan-lib.pl         - function library used by vlan.cgi and vlanconfig

